    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ぜんたーい、止まれ！
右向け～、右っ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Attention! Stop! Face right! Right!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282244</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Cless&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282332</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;ヴァルハラ&lt;White&gt;の方は
片付いたのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So you've been dismissed from
the mission in &lt;Red&gt;Valhalla&lt;White&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282452</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いや。いよいよ
総力を投じることになって
援軍を頼みに戻ってきたんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm afraid not. We are strengthening
our forces to provide backup.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282560</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>絶対、ぶっ潰してこいよ。
グリッドの両親のかたきだ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Make them pay! What they've done
to Grid's parents is unforgivable...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282656</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>グリッド……？
&lt;Chester&gt;んちにいる
子どもか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Grid...? You mean the kid
that's over at your house?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ。あいつの両親……
『シグルド』に殺されたんだよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Same kid. Those bastards killed his parents...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あいつら、やること、
めちゃくちゃだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He's the proof this has
gone way too far!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>敵味方関係なく
無差別に殺しまくって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Doesn't matter if you're friend or
foe. They kill as they please!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282948</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この子たちは？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who are these kids?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283048</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ……おまえの客だよ。
話を聞きたいんだってさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They're visitors. They've been waiting
to have a word with you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283152</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうか。
でも、ごめんよ、
今は戦いの準備をしなきゃ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see. I'm sorry, but that'll have to
wait. We're preparing for an assault. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんなの、
したっぱに任せとけよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Really, now? Just leave
someone else in charge.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>大体、&lt;Mint&gt;とも
ろくに会ってないんだろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hell, have you met with &lt;Mint&gt; yet?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283380</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>彼女も忙しい
みたいだから……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That girl is very busy herself...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283856</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>すみません！　&lt;Cless&gt;さん、
ちょっといいですか！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Excuse me! Mister &lt;Cless&gt;, could
you spare me a second?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、はい、今行きます！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes! I'll be there right away!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284016</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>すまない、
ちょっと行ってくる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I apologize, I really have to go.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284120</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、おい……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>H-Hey! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284120</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まったく、あいつ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What crawled up his ass, now?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284192</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんか大変そうだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This really does look like
a dangerous situation.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284292</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;さんと&lt;Mint&gt;さんって
……恋人なのかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mister &lt;Cless&gt; and Miss &lt;Mint&gt;
are...lovers are they?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284400</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　あっと……
そういや、んなこと
本に書いてたかも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wh-What? W-Well... It's not
like...those types of things
are written in books...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284472</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんか曖昧だね、きミ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I feel something's off here...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284576</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だってオレ、
なんかそーゆーの
よくわかんねーし……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't look at me! I don't know
the first thing about it, either!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284688</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ね、わたしたちで
&lt;Cless&gt;さんたちを
会わせてあげらんないかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, why don't we reunite those two?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285176</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>会わせるったって
どうすんだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And how exactly do you plan to do that?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285280</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふたりのお手伝いするとか。
忙しくて会えないんでしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We can take over for them so
they have some free time.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285580</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『なりきり士』の力を使えば、
お手伝いできること
なにかあるんじゃない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I mean, aren't Roleplayer
powers meant to help
people in need like this?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285648</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうかぁ～……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You sure about this?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285748</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_042&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ね、とにかく&lt;Mint&gt;さんに
会いに行ってみない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, why don't we meet with &lt;Mint&gt;
first? We can go from there.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285812</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_010_043&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuru!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
